headline: Welltower Secures Credit Rating Upgrade From S&P & Moody's
summary: In a positive development, WELL achieves an 'A-' credit rating from S&P and an 'A3' credit rating from Moody's, based on its operational excellence and balance sheet strength.

headline: 10 Stocks of the S&P 500 ETF Up More Than 20% in Q1
summary: While many stocks in the S&P 500 ETF posted dismal performance in the just-concluded quarter, we discuss some that rose by more than 20%.
